<h6 class="ltx_title ltx_title_abstract">Abstract</h6>
<p id="id1" class="ltx_p">We show that everyone can understand quantum mechanics, only if he
rejects the following prejudice, namely classical continuous
motion (CCM) is the only possible and objective motion of
particles.</p>
</div>
<div id="p1" class="ltx_para">
<p id="p1.1" class="ltx_p ltx_align_center"><span id="p1.1.1" class="ltx_text ltx_font_bold" style="font-size:173%;">Everyone can understand quantum mechanics</span></p>
</div>
