<div id="p5" class="ltx_para">
<p id="p5.1" class="ltx_p"><span id="p5.1.1" class="ltx_text ltx_font_italic">I think I can safely say that nobody today understands
quantum mechanics. â€”â€”Feynman (1965)</span></p>
</div>
<div id="p6" class="ltx_para">
